{"tid":1300073,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各位仲諗緊今個星期日去唔去遊行既手足入一入黎!7月14日，沙田見","createTime":"2019-07-09T09:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T03:09:40.000Z","uid":147696,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2504610fb38b2f48280b71a5a3a5d43c8b7a8d82","tid":1300073,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:01:58.000Z","msg":"有好多人覺得，沙田外憂內患都唔係好嚴重呀，唔似屯門有大媽，TKO有CCTVB,上水冇民生所需...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，新東沙田係全港<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">DQ之冠</span></span>，而眾所周知，新東既選民係出哂名泛民既票倉，15同18年補選都可以重奪議席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話，如果將來18區都出黎遊行，呢次遊行其實係一個index去反映返除左對5大訴求不滿外，仲睇到地區市民既向心力同對非建制既支持度，同埋作為其他區既傍樣，試諗下，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果連我地都冇咩人去既話，後果會點?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再者，上星期九龍遊行好多人都舉牌舉紙去盡我地好客之道，向中國人解釋自由既可貴，講講一國發生咩野事。而沙田新城市廣場，係中國遊客既加持下成功變做<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">全港最多(中國人)人流既廣場</span></span>，文宣既手足，導遊們，識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，多謝林鄭今日又再一次激發起我地行動既心，今朝睇完真係火撚滾。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要求回應五加二訴求</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiqwaAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiqwaAa.jpg&h=aa9f27ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bOhQAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bOhQAa.jpg&h=de943052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aNxKvAb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaNxKvAb.jpg&h=74586b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZAgjjtx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZAgjjtx.jpg&h=3a172a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7cFOmT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7cFOmT.jpg&h=aeb7c947&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bb9bd801e30b1ef5d878fa56a32b84ba3742703","tid":1300073,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:04:00.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bf1d4a1580d0e155f5e1531dace75e2563fa5c","tid":1300073,"uid":129805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0933e8b347cb502cc7eafbc2716917a607a7cad7","tid":1300073,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"推呀，推到全世界沙田人同我出黎"},{"pid":"fb883cd21d48188f97f9c869d2f6ac9318c8c83c","tid":1300073,"uid":267801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"撤回，撤回，不撤不休。"},{"pid":"c1da51c6972255eca2968227df0a466256481ad4","tid":1300073,"uid":225585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"ae2aa6232c446b1dfe90b513429050498819d039","tid":1300073,"uid":93115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f